01:35:35.999 --> 01:35:38.043
I don't want to
get married to you.

1432
01:35:38.085 --> 01:35:40.420
Definitely don't want
to have your babies.

1433
01:35:40.462 --> 01:35:42.672
Whatever happens tomorrow,
we've had today.

1434
01:35:49.471 --> 01:35:51.848
And if we should bump into
each other sometime in the future,

1435
01:35:51.890 --> 01:35:53.475
well, that's fine, too.

1436
01:35:55.018 --> 01:35:56.979
We'll be friends.

1437
01:35:57.020 --> 01:35:58.563
Yeah, right.

1438
01:36:05.570 --> 01:36:07.990
Or, you know,
on the other hand...

1439
01:36:10.617 --> 01:36:11.701
Go on.

1440
01:36:14.245 --> 01:36:16.372
Well, my parents
don't arrive until later.

1441
01:36:18.333 --> 01:36:20.085
So?

1442
01:36:20.127 --> 01:36:22.754
So, well, the flat's empty.

1443
01:36:25.048 --> 01:36:27.717
You know, if you wanted
to finish what we started.

1444
01:36:29.594 --> 01:36:30.971
What? Sober?

1445
01:36:31.596 --> 01:36:32.555
Mmm-hmm.

1446
01:36:34.141 --> 01:36:35.391
And in daylight.

1447
01:36:39.980 --> 01:36:40.814
Race you!

1448
01:36:56.746 --> 01:37:00.250
Do you want a piggy-back,
you old man?

1449
01:37:00.291 --> 01:37:03.712
It's these shoes. There's no
blooming grip on these things.

1450
01:37:03.753 --> 01:37:05.421
Here, come here, you.

1451
01:37:10.260 --> 01:37:11.178
Did you come up here with Emma?

1452
01:37:11.220 --> 01:37:12.929
Yeah, once.

1453
01:37:12.971 --> 01:37:14.472
That was a long time ago now.

1454
01:37:15.891 --> 01:37:17.433
Do you miss her?

1455
01:37:17.475 --> 01:37:18.560
Well, of course, I do.

1456
01:37:20.187 --> 01:37:23.857
She was...
She was my best friend.

1457
01:37:23.899 --> 01:37:26.151
Who's your best friend now then?

1458
01:37:26.193 --> 01:37:28.486
Well, you are, of course.
Come here.

1459
01:37:30.030 --> 01:37:31.364
Why, who's yours?

1460
01:37:32.991 --> 01:37:34.993
I think it's probably Mum.

1461
01:37:38.997 --> 01:37:39.873
Yeah.

1462
01:37:42.625 --> 01:37:44.377
I'm not so
terrible though, am I?

1463
01:37:44.419 --> 01:37:45.879
I'm not answering that.

1464
01:37:50.633 --> 01:37:52.219
You know what you are.

1465
01:38:19.121 --> 01:38:21.164
It's just round the corner.
This way.

1466
01:38:22.624 --> 01:38:23.792
Oh, Dexter!

1467
01:38:23.833 --> 01:38:25.294
Damn it, they're early.

1468
01:38:27.837 --> 01:38:29.214
You're early.

1469
01:38:29.256 --> 01:38:31.466
We thought we'd surprise you.

1470
01:38:31.507 --> 01:38:32.842
Clearly, we have.

1471
01:38:35.511 --> 01:38:38.014
Mum, Dad, this is Emma Morley.
Morley.

1472
01:38:38.056 --> 01:38:39.515
Hello. Pleased to meet you.

1473
01:38:39.557 --> 01:38:41.643
Emma, you'll join us
for tea, yes?

1474
01:38:41.684 --> 01:38:44.813
No, no, thanks.
I should leave you to it.

1475
01:38:44.854 --> 01:38:47.440
Are you going to go? Yeah. Well,

1476
01:38:47.482 --> 01:38:49.901
pleasure to meet you and...

1477
01:38:49.943 --> 01:38:52.279
Well, have a nice life.

1478
01:38:52.321 --> 01:38:53.280
Okay.

1479
01:39:00.078 --> 01:39:02.705
I'm sorry. Did we
just interrupt something?

1480
01:39:02.747 --> 01:39:06.084
No, no.
Emma's just a good friend.

1481
01:39:07.877 --> 01:39:08.878
Weren't you
wearing this yesterday?

1482
01:39:09.879 --> 01:39:10.880
The rascal.

1483
01:39:16.886 --> 01:39:18.638
Emma! Em!

1484
01:39:18.680 --> 01:39:21.099
Em, wait! Wait, wait.

1485
01:39:23.185 --> 01:39:26.313
Look, I need your phone number.

1486
01:39:26.355 --> 01:39:29.899
My number? Right. Of course.

1487
01:39:29.941 --> 01:39:31.734
Look, I'm so sorry
about all of that.

1488
01:39:31.776 --> 01:39:34.404
I wasn't expecting them until
after we... Well, you know.

1489
01:39:35.905 --> 01:39:36.906
Right.

1490
01:39:38.241 --> 01:39:39.326
This is me in Edinburgh.

1491
01:39:39.368 --> 01:39:40.493
Right.

1492
01:39:41.703 --> 01:39:43.163
My parents' number

1493
01:39:44.789 --> 01:39:46.666
and their address just in case.

1494
01:39:46.708 --> 01:39:48.960
Right.

1495
01:39:49.002 --> 01:39:50.753
Oh. Dad's got
a fax machine at work.

1496
01:39:50.795 --> 01:39:53.298
Just the phone number's fine.

1497
01:39:53.340 --> 01:39:54.383
Thank you.

1498
01:40:25.830 --> 01:40:26.831
Look, I've got to go.

1499
01:40:26.873 --> 01:40:27.749
I know.

1500
01:40:31.086 --> 01:40:32.379
But we will see
each other again.

1501
01:40:32.421 --> 01:40:33.629
I know we will.

1502
01:40:36.425 --> 01:40:37.426
Goodbye, Dex.

1503
01:40:38.009 --> 01:40:39.052
Goodbye.

1504
01:40:40.511 --> 01:40:41.554
Goodbye.

